Class PspiFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • PspiFile

  • public class PspiFile
extends java.lang.Object
    The purpose of this class is read a pspi file, create all the PstFolder objects within the file, and then create all the PstFile objects that are contained in the pspi file and add them to their respective PstFolder.
